{"tid":142964,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"震驚十三億人的老麥兵法","createTime":"2017-03-04T08:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T09:05:46.000Z","uid":84136,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68e093334eb7c3368d7946ca3667fe7c8e730f2d","tid":142964,"uid":84136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"有人去老麥係因為平 食24蚊餐<br />\n但我對味道 食材 烹調有一份執著<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">豬柳強</span> <span style=\"color: orange;\">脆香雞翼</span> <span style=\"color: violet;\">奶昔</span><br />\n先係我心目中實至名歸既一個餐<br />\n如果可以既話 我希望可以加多一塊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">薯餅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不過<br />\n而家豬柳強個兩塊包做乜鳩？勁難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9589b2821ecbf62bd5106ce8761b04a676bbbdf2","tid":142964,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"十蚊你想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c8a0c919daee442e2bec9d5314a94ea5d1dde6","tid":142964,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:05:46.000Z","msg":"有無試過用唱歌既方法叫M記"}]}